<td class="" style=""><a href="/wiki/Multi-paradigm_programming_language" title="Multi-paradigm programming language">multi-paradigm</a>: <a href="/wiki/Procedural_programming" title="Procedural programming">procedural</a>, <a href="/wiki/Imperative_programming_language" title="Imperative programming language" class="mw-redirect">imperative</a>, <a href="/wiki/Structured_programming" title="Structured programming">structured</a>, <a href="/wiki/Object-oriented_programming" title="Object-oriented programming">object-oriented</a></td>
